title: Grateful Dead Live at Red Rocks Amphitheatre on 1987-08-12
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Good Time Blues, Cumberland Blues-> Mexicali Blues, Friend Of The Devil, My Brother Esau, Bird Song, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Wharf Rat-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: The Mighty Quinn
